2010-03-04  Peter Breitenlohner  <peb@mppmu.mpg.de>

	* Makefile.am (ft-libs): Use again '--libs' instead of
	'--libtool', because otherwise required Mac OS X libraries are
	absent. Use sed to convert '-L$(abs_builddir) -lfreetype' into
	'$(abs_builddir)/libfreetype.la'.

